data.description: Fabulous home located in a well established neighborhood of Creekside Oaks. No neighbors in the back, which is used to be a Fairway. This 3 bed 2 bath home features lots of natural light, vaulted ceilings in living room and the kitchen. This nice and bright kitchen features Tons of cabinets, gorgeous countertops, stainless steel appliances, Ceramic tiled flooring and a breakfast bar. Formal dining room/bonus room is located right off the kitchen and also features a sliding door that leads to the backyard. Spacious master bedroom features coffered ceilings, lighted ceiling fan, tiles in the bath and stylish fixtures in the bathroom. It also has its own private entrance to SUNROOM! The additional bedrooms also feature lighted ceiling fans and they share an updated bath in the hallway. You will love the Large Screened in PORCH on the back to enjoy the breezy evenings! Call today for your private showings!
